steps.name: Inventory User: Create and Submit Material Request
Text Total Stock Value is visible
Fill Items in Material Request Based on Sales Order
Click on "Sales Order" option in context menu
Fill SAL-ORD-2026-00001 Name into search field
Click on "Yes" in the modal window
Purchase User: Create and Submit Purchase Order
Text Purchase Order Trends is visible
Fill Items in Material Request Based on Sales Order
Click on "Material Request" option in context menu
Fill MAT-MR-2026-00001 Name into search field
Click on "Yes" in the modal window
Assert Document Status is "To Receive and Bill"
Purchase User: Create and Submit Purchase Receipt
Text Total Stock Value is visible
Fill Items in Purchase Receipt Based on Purchase Order
Click on "Purchase Order" option in context menu
Fill PUR-ORD-2026-00001 Name into search field
Click on "Yes" in the modal window
Assert Sales Order status, delivery_status and billing_status
Sales Order status should be "To Deliver and Bill"
Sales Order delivery_status should be "Not Delivered"
Sales Order billing_status should be "Not Billed"
